A. J. Langer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._J._Langer 0 Allison Joy Courtenay, Countess of Devon (née Langer, born May 22, 1974), commonly known as A. J. Langer, is an American former actress most notable for her role as Rayanne Graff on the television series My So-Called Life.
